      "uid": 0,
      "comment": "NPC — Erik Douglas (Physical Description)",
      "key": [
        "Erik",
        "his appearance",
        "what he looks like",
        "describe him"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Erik Douglas possesses a towering, immovable physical presence that dominates any room he enters. He is built like a dormant volcano, broad-shouldered and immaculately groomed, always wearing bespoke, sharply tailored dark suits that function as corporate armor. His face is a mask of sculpted stone, characterized by a strong jawline and pale, piercing eyes that evaluate everything as a tactical threat. He moves with slow, terrifying deliberation, never rushing, because the world waits for him. He carries the sterile, cold scent of expensive cedar cologne and polished steel.",
